I'm trying to read what
it says at the top.

01:20:54.240 --> 01:20:58.860
To leave the white walls gray or
paint them white is vandalism.

01:20:58.860 --> 01:21:01.440
Your environment is changing.

01:21:01.440 --> 01:21:03.960
Get yourself, get
together with it.

01:21:03.960 --> 01:21:06.750
No one knows better how
to create your environment

01:21:06.750 --> 01:21:08.050
than you do.

01:21:08.050 --> 01:21:11.620
Does your environment
respond to your needs?

01:21:11.620 --> 01:21:17.290
What a statement of
anarchy invitation.

