This is a time when
the form of the city

01:21:34.900 --> 01:21:38.890
was politically significant
to the students in the two

01:21:38.890 --> 01:21:39.635
universities.

01:21:39.635 --> 01:21:40.135
Next.

01:21:44.080 --> 01:21:48.335
Herrey was MIT's
real estate boss.

01:21:52.570 --> 01:21:53.070
Next.

01:21:55.902 --> 01:22:00.310
The university's response,
the University and the City,

01:22:00.310 --> 01:22:02.540
Harvard's University
and the City.

01:22:02.540 --> 01:22:06.620
These are all University reports
saying how great things are.

01:22:06.620 --> 01:22:07.120
Next.

01:22:11.270 --> 01:22:15.210
There's a thesis done
by Monika Unger called

01:22:15.210 --> 01:22:22.280
"The Politics of Urbanity" on
the history of the attempts

01:22:22.280 --> 01:22:26.390
in Brussels, after
the Manhattan plan,

01:22:26.390 --> 01:22:31.380
to respond vigorously
to the plan.

01:22:31.380 --> 01:22:39.440
The plan was to internationalize
Brussels, with tall buildings,

01:22:39.440 --> 01:22:42.740
as the center of
the European market.

01:22:42.740 --> 01:22:47.840
And here are posters
emanating from the society

01:22:47.840 --> 01:22:55.340
itself saying no to Carrere, no
to Venturi, no to Chernikhov,

01:22:55.340 --> 01:22:58.335
no to Kroll.

01:22:58.335 --> 01:22:58.835
Next.

01:23:03.430 --> 01:23:07.420
Posters which set out the way
in which local neighborhoods

01:23:07.420 --> 01:23:10.120
should be fixed.

01:23:10.120 --> 01:23:16.630
A whole set of items like
this monthly magazine

01:23:16.630 --> 01:23:18.640
for the urban
struggles, information

01:23:18.640 --> 01:23:21.280
about the development
projects at Brussels,

01:23:21.280 --> 01:23:23.740
the work of
inhabitants' committees,

01:23:23.740 --> 01:23:26.470
theaters, schools
of architecture,

01:23:26.470 --> 01:23:31.840
cinema, arts museums,
all being formed together

01:23:31.840 --> 01:23:37.120
to form a protest environment
with educational material

01:23:37.120 --> 01:23:40.430
in the form of daily
posters on the left.

01:23:40.430 --> 01:23:40.930
Next.

01:23:43.720 --> 01:23:47.620
So all of this
stuff is an attempt

01:23:47.620 --> 01:23:50.500
to influence the
form of the city,

01:23:50.500 --> 01:23:54.540
often stopping negative
things from happening.